<item>
            <title>[AVRO-1753] Support for import in avpr file from avsc schema file</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AVRO-1753</link>
                <project id="12310911" key="AVRO">Apache Avro</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have two schema file&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;First is position.avsc&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;{&lt;br/&gt;
&quot;type&quot;:&quot;enum&quot;, &quot;name&quot;: &quot;Position&quot;, &quot;namespace&quot;: &quot;avro.examples.baseball&quot;,&lt;br/&gt;
    &quot;symbols&quot;: &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;quot;P&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;C&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;B1&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;B2&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;B3&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;SS&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;LF&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;CF&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;RF&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DH&amp;quot;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
}&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Second is player.avsc&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;{&lt;br/&gt;
&quot;type&quot;:&quot;record&quot;, &quot;name&quot;:&quot;Player&quot;, &quot;namespace&quot;: &quot;avro.examples.baseball&quot;,&lt;br/&gt;
  &quot;fields&quot;: [&lt;br/&gt;
   &lt;/p&gt;
{&quot;name&quot;: &quot;number&quot;, &quot;type&quot;: &quot;int&quot;}
&lt;p&gt;,&lt;br/&gt;
   &lt;/p&gt;
{&quot;name&quot;: &quot;first_name&quot;, &quot;type&quot;: &quot;string&quot;}
&lt;p&gt;,&lt;br/&gt;
   &lt;/p&gt;
{&quot;name&quot;: &quot;last_name&quot;, &quot;type&quot;: &quot;string&quot;}
&lt;p&gt;,&lt;br/&gt;
   {&quot;name&quot;: &quot;position&quot;, &quot;type&quot;: &lt;/p&gt;
{&quot;type&quot;: &quot;array&quot;, &quot;items&quot;: &quot;avro.examples.baseball.Position&quot;}
&lt;p&gt; }&lt;br/&gt;
  ]&lt;br/&gt;
}&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I can import these schemas in avdl&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;@namespace(&quot;avro.examples.baseball&quot;)&lt;br/&gt;
protocol Baseball {&lt;br/&gt;
   import schema &quot;position.avsc&quot;;&lt;br/&gt;
   import schema &quot;player.avsc&quot;;&lt;br/&gt;
}&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But I want to define above protocol in json and import those schemas in protocol file.&lt;br/&gt;
This will be helpful for reusability of schema&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
